@startuml fig-S14-e2-message-flow
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title S14 — E2 Path: DV Update Exchange and Convergence After Link Failure

participant "r1" as R1 #C8E6C9
participant "r2" as R2 #C8E6C9
participant "r3" as R3 #C8E6C9

== INITIAL DV EXCHANGE (convergence) ==
R1 -[#1565C0]-> R2 : DV1 {hA:0, r2:1, r3:2, hB:3}
R1 -[#1565C0]-> R3 : DV1 {hA:0, r2:1, r3:2, hB:3}
R2 -[#1565C0]-> R1 : DV1 {hA:1, r2:0, r3:1, hB:2}
R2 -[#1565C0]-> R3 : DV1 {hA:1, r2:0, r3:1, hB:2}
R3 -[#1565C0]-> R1 : DV1 {hA:2, r2:1, r3:0, hB:1}
R3 -[#1565C0]-> R2 : DV1 {hA:2, r2:1, r3:0, hB:1}

note over R1, R3 : Routing tables converged\nhA→r1→r2→r3→hB (cost 3)

== DATA FORWARDING (overlay) ==
R1 -> R2 : DATA1 src=hA dst=hB payload
R2 -> R3 : DATA1 src=hA dst=hB payload
note right of R3 : Delivered to hB

== LINK FAILURE: r1—r2 DOWN ==
note over R1, R2 #FFCDD2 : Link r1↔r2 fails

|||

== TRIGGERED UPDATE (anti-loop) ==
R1 -[#E53935]-> R3 : DV1 {r2:INF}\n(POISON reverse)
R3 -[#1565C0]-> R1 : DV1 {r2:1, hB:1}

note over R1, R3 : Reconverged\nhA→r1→r3→hB (cost via backup)

== DATA FORWARDING (new path) ==
R1 -> R3 : DATA1 src=hA dst=hB payload
note right of R3 : Delivered to hB via backup

legend right
  DV1: periodic updates with distance vectors
  POISON/SPLITH: anti-loop evidence in PCAP
  DATA1: overlay forwarding hop-by-hop
  Validates R1–R4 in S14.json
endlegend
@enduml
